title: MONDAY 6/7 - JULIO JONES TITANS UP
itunes:title: MONDAY 6/7 - JULIO JONES TITANS UP
description:
Julio Jones (0:08) dealt to the Titans, here what GM Jon Robinson (0:52) has to say about the move. Bill Belichick (1:24) talks about the development of rookie QB Mac Jones. Tua Tagovailoa admits to struggling with the Miami offense in his rookie season. Head coach Brian Flores (2:19) explains. Giants head coach Joe Judge (2:58) talks about his new big-time receiver Kenny Golladay. Plus, Robert Saleh (3:56) liking what he's seen from first-round pick Zach Wilson
